Hold the BOOTSEL button on the Raspberry Pi Pico, plug the USB connection on the Pico in to the development machine, then release the BOOTSEL button.

if you run pico_setup.sh, it will not install minicom because we dont want vscode

hello_usb.uf2 NOT hello_serial.uf2
minicom -b 115200 -o -D /dev/ttyACM0

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NHwMJZwRo7k

